Oppressed by her family setting, dead-end school prospects and the boys
law in the neighborhood, Marieme starts a new life after meeting a group
of 3 free-spirited girls. She changes her name, her dress code, and quits
school to be accepted in the gang, hoping that this will be a way to
freedom.
